snippet.title: Ori and the Blind Forest: Definitive Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Winner of several prestigious awards, “Ori and the Blind Forest” tells the tale of a young orphan destined for heroics, through a visually stunning Action-Platformer crafted by Moon Studios. 

The Definitive Edition is packed with new and additional content including new areas, new abilities, more story sequences, multiple difficulty modes, fast travel between areas and much more!
